<i> she couldn't understand.</i>

59:37.808 --> 59:38.974
<i> She was also quite illiterate.</i>

59:38.976 --> 59:44.846
<i> She couldn't read</i>
<i> the signs and tracks at all.</i>

59:53.089 --> 59:56.258
We're waiting for a bus?

59:59.963 --> 01:00:03.065
